  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "89d76164-164a-420e-b0d1-05067386883e",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Artifact Lancea",
      "effect": "You can Set this card from your hand to your Spell & Trap Zone as a Spell. During your opponent's turn, if this Set card in the Spell & Trap Zone is destroyed and sent to your GY: Special Summon it. During your opponent's turn (Quick Effect): You can Tribute this card from your hand or face-up field; neither player can banish cards for the rest of this turn."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Lancea - Art\u00e9fact",
      "effect": "Vous pouvez Poser cette carte depuis votre main dans votre Zone Magie & Pi\u00e8ge comme Magie. Durant le tour de votre adversaire, si cette carte Pos\u00e9e dans la Zone Magie & Pi\u00e8ge est d\u00e9truite et envoy\u00e9e \u00e0 votre Cimeti\u00e8re : Invoquez-la Sp\u00e9cialement. Durant le tour de votre adversaire (Effet Rapide) : vous pouvez Sacrifier cette carte depuis votre main ou Terrain face recto ; le reste de ce tour, aucun joueur ne peut bannir de cartes."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Artefakt Longinuslanze",
      "effect": "Du kannst diese Karte als Zauber von deiner Hand in deine Zauber- & Fallenzone setzen. W\u00e4hrend des Spielzugs deines Gegners, falls diese gesetzte Karte in der Zauber- & Fallenzone zerst\u00f6rt und auf deinen Friedhof gelegt wird: Beschw\u00f6re sie als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung. W\u00e4hrend des Spielzugs deines Gegners (Schnelleffekt): Du kannst diese Karte von deiner Hand oder offen von deiner Spielfeldseite als Tribut anbieten; f\u00fcr den Rest dieses Spielzugs kann kein Spieler Karten verbannen."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Artefatto - Lancea",
      "effect": "Puoi Posizionare questa carta dalla tua mano nella tua Zona Magie & Trappole come una Magia. Durante il turno del tuo avversario, se questa carta Posizionata nella Zona Magie & Trappole viene distrutta e mandata al tuo Cimitero: Evocala Specialmente. Durante il turno del tuo avversario (Effetto Rapido): puoi offrire come Tributo questa carta dalla tua mano o Terreno scoperto; nessun giocatore pu\u00f2 bandire carte per il resto di questo turno."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Artefato Lan\u00e7a do Destino",
      "effect": "Voc\u00ea pode Baixar este card da sua m\u00e3o na sua Zona de Magias & Armadilhas como uma Magia. Durante o turno do seu oponente, se este card Baixado na Zona de Magias & Armadilhas for destru\u00eddo e enviado para o seu Cemit\u00e9rio: Invoque-o por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Especial. Durante o turno do seu oponente (Efeito R\u00e1pido): voc\u00ea pode oferecer este card como Tributo da sua m\u00e3o ou do campo com a face para cima; nenhum duelista pode banir cards pelo resto deste turno."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Artefacto Lancea",
      "effect": "Puedes Colocar esta carta en tu mano en tu Zona de Magia y Trampas como una M\u00e1gica. Durante el turno de tu adversario, si esta carta Colocada en la Zona de Magia y Trampas es destruida y mandada a tu Cementerio: Inv\u00f3cala de Modo Especial. Durante el turno de tu adversario (Efecto R\u00e1pido): puedes Sacrificar esta carta en tu mano o Campo boca arriba; por el resto de este turno, ning\u00fan jugador puede desterrar cartas."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u30a2\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\u30d5\u30a1\u30af\u30c8\uff0d\u30ed\u30f3\u30ae\u30cc\u30b9",
      "effect": "\u2460\uff1a\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u306f\u9b54\u6cd5\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u6271\u3044\u3068\u3057\u3066\u624b\u672d\u304b\u3089\u9b54\u6cd5\uff06\u7f60\u30be\u30fc\u30f3\u306b\u30bb\u30c3\u30c8\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u2461\uff1a\u9b54\u6cd5\uff06\u7f60\u30be\u30fc\u30f3\u306b\u30bb\u30c3\u30c8\u3055\u308c\u305f\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\u76f8\u624b\u30bf\u30fc\u30f3\u306b\u7834\u58ca\u3055\u308c\u5893\u5730\u3078\u9001\u3089\u308c\u305f\u5834\u5408\u306b\u767a\u52d5\u3059\u308b\u3002\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u3092\u7279\u6b8a\u53ec\u559a\u3059\u308b\u3002\u2462\uff1a\u76f8\u624b\u30bf\u30fc\u30f3\u306b\u3001\u624b\u672d\u30fb\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u306e\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u3092\u30ea\u30ea\u30fc\u30b9\u3057\u3066\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u3053\u306e\u30bf\u30fc\u30f3\u3001\u304a\u4e92\u3044\u306b\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u3092\u9664\u5916\u3067\u304d\u306a\u3044\u3002"
    },
    "ko": {
      "name": "\uc544\ud2f0\ud329\ud2b8\uff0d\ub871\uae30\ub204\uc2a4",
      "effect": "\u2460: \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\ub294 \ub9c8\ubc95 \uce74\ub4dc\ub85c \ucde8\uae09\ud558\uace0 \ud328\uc5d0\uc11c \ub9c8\ubc95 & \ud568\uc815 \uc874\uc5d0 \uc138\ud2b8\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \u2461: \ub9c8\ubc95 & \ud568\uc815 \uc874\uc5d0 \uc138\ud2b8\ub41c \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\uac00 \uc0c1\ub300 \ud134\uc5d0 \ud30c\uad34\ub418\uc5b4 \ubb18\uc9c0\ub85c \ubcf4\ub0b4\uc84c\uc744 \uacbd\uc6b0\uc5d0 \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud55c\ub2e4. \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\ub97c \ud2b9\uc218 \uc18c\ud658\ud55c\ub2e4. \u2462: \uc0c1\ub300 \ud134\uc5d0, \ud328 / \ud544\ub4dc\uc758 \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\ub97c \ub9b4\ub9ac\uc2a4\ud558\uace0 \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \uc774 \ud134\uc5d0, \uc11c\ub85c \uce74\ub4dc\ub97c \uc81c\uc678\ud560 \uc218 \uc5c6\ub2e4."
    },
    "zh-CN": {
